posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 70625967', 'Rent: $2,600 / Month', 'Beds: 1', 'Bath: 1', 'Available Date: 09/01/2022', 'Pet: Cats Allowed', 'Rent Includes:: Heat, Hot Water', 'Amazing one bed in fantastic Fenway location.', 'Walking distance to Longwood, easily accessible to Northeastern & other colleges, and steps to Fenway Park.', 'The Fenway apartments, located in turn of the century brick buildings, are a fantastic reflection of the neighborhood.', 'Some units have been renovated to include features such as granite or quartz countertops, hardwood floors and modern kitchens and bathrooms, while others have that old Boston charm.', 'All of the buildings have central laundry facilities and offer parking at competitive rates.', 'Video Tour: <URL>', '• 24 hour emergency service', '• Common laundry facilities', '• High speed internet access ready', '• Single Stream recycling', '• Modern windows and enhanced exterior lighting', '• Competitively-priced off-street parking', '• Bicycle Storage', 'PLEASE RESPOND WITH YOUR ACTUAL EMAIL ADDRESS OR PHONE NUMBER TO ENSURE YOU RECEIVE MY RESPONSE!', 'THANK YOU!', 'Call Aidan at 201-449-4090 or respond with your name, phone number, and email for further information or to schedule a showing!', 'Aidan Pink', 'Real Estate Agent', 'East Coast Realty']
